# Identity-Locked Learning Validation Report
Report Date: April 27, 2026
Validation Task: rerun_identity_locked_rigorous_validation_v1 (test3.json)

## 1. Executive Summary
The implementation of `identity_lock_v1` has successfully stabilized groove selection, reducing the average `groove_switch_count` from over 100 to ~10 per run. However, rigorous multi-seed testing reveals that this stability has not yet translated into consistent trajectory learning. In many cases, the continuation mismatch increased across repeated passes, suggesting that the current feedback mechanism may be over-correcting or misaligned.

